title: Supercrooks 01-04 (2012) (Complete) (theProletariat-DCP)
description:
This torrent includes the 4 issue miniseries published by Marvel, written Mark Millar with some amazing art by Leinil Francis Yu.  Both c2c and noAds versions are provided.
========================================================


When The Market Is Flooded With Competition And The Authorities Are Always On Your Tail, What's An All-American Supervillain To Do? Go To Spain, Of Course!


Thanks goes to theProletariat for these scans.
